    "body": "A great and beautiful example of an application that shows all the metrics in a clear and concise way to the user is the [Balance Manager app](https://manager.balance.io/):\r\n\r\nThis could serve as a great foundation for a new and improved send transaction flow which isn't terribly different than the current design.\r\n\r\nThere's nothing about gas or gas costs, only information on the speed of the transaction and the fees for that delivery speed. Along with allowing the user to enter the amount in either ETH or $$ which automatically converts the values for them.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1206980/39995015-2b1960b8-57cf-11e8-9c2a-6ac39df5189c.png)\r\n",
